WATCH: Adamson cheerdancers finish strong tribal routine ABS-CBN News Posted at Nov 19 2016 04:33 PM 
Share Watch also in iWantv or TFC.tv 
MANILA, Philippines â€” Watch how Adamson University, using a tribal-themed performance, pulled off a near-perfect routine at the 2016 UAAP Cheerdance Competition. 
Finishing seventh in last year's competition, Adamson made a strong case for the championship donning blue and white native costumes and hitting the cheerdance floor with a Polynesian-inspired production.
